ion] from ''[[The Encyclopedia of World History]]'' Sixth Edition, Peter N. Stearns (general editor), 2001 [[Houghton Mifflin Company]], at Bartleby.com.\n* [[Charles R. H. Tripp|Tripp, Charles]]. \"Iraq and the 1948 War: mirror of Iraq's disorder.\" in Rogan and Shlaim. ''The War for Palestine''. pp.&nbsp;125\u201350.\n{{Refend}}\n\n==Further reading==\n\n===History===\n* Aloni, Shlomo (2001). ''Arab-Israeli Air Wars 1947\u201382''. [[Osprey Publishing]]. {{ISBN|978-1-84176-294-4}}\n* [[Morris Beckman (writer)|Beckman, Morris]] (1999). ''The Jewish Brigade: An Army With Two Masters, 1944\u201345''. Sarpedon Publishers. {{ISBN|978-1-86227-423-5}}\n* <span id=\"Ben-Ami\">[[Shlomo Ben-Ami|Ben-Ami, Shlomo]] (2006). ''[[Scars of War, Wounds of Peace: The Israeli-Arab Tragedy]]''. [[Oxford University Press]]. {{ISBN|978-0-19-518158-6}}</span>\n* [[Meron Benvenisti|Benvenisti, Meron]] (2002). ''Sacred Landscape''. [[University of California Press]]. {{ISBN|978-0-520-23422-2}}\n* [[Simha Flapan|Flapan, Simha]] (1987), ''The Birth of Israel: Myths and Realities'', [[Pantheon Books]], New York.\n* [[Martin Gilbert|Gilbert, Martin]] (1976). ''The Arab-Israeli Conflict: Its History in Maps'' [[Weidenfeld & Nicolson]]. {{ISBN|978-0-297-77241-5}}\n* [[Joshua Landis|Landis, Joshua]]. \"Syria and the Palestine War: fighting King 'Abdullah's 'Greater Syria plan.'\" Rogan and Shlaim. ''The War for Palestine''. 178\u2013205.\n* [[Nur-eldeen Masalha|Masalha, Nur]] (1992). ''[[Expulsion of the Palestinians: The Concept of 'Transfer' in Zionist Political Thought, 1882\u20131948]]'', [[Institute for Palestine Studies]], {{ISBN|978-0-88728-235-5}}\n* [[Ilan Papp\u00e9|Pappe, Ilan]] (2006), ''[[The Ethnic Cleansing of Palestine]]'', [[Oneworld Publications]], Oxford, England, {{ISBN|978-1-85168-467-0}}\n* Reiter, Yitzhak, \"National Minority, Regional Majority: Palestinian Arabs Versus Jews in Israel\" (''Syracuse Studies on Peace and Conflict Resolution''), (2009) Syracuse Univ Press (Sd)