 Press]]. {{ISBN|978-0-520-23422-2}}\n* [[Simha Flapan|Flapan, Simha]] (1987), ''The Birth of Israel: Myths and Realities'', [[Pantheon Books]], New York.\n* [[Martin Gilbert|Gilbert, Martin]] (1976). ''The Arab-Israeli Conflict: Its History in Maps'' [[Weidenfeld & Nicolson]]. {{ISBN|978-0-297-77241-5}}\n* [[Joshua Landis|Landis, Joshua]]. \"Syria and the Palestine War: fighting King 'Abdullah's 'Greater Syria plan.'\" Rogan and Shlaim. ''The War for Palestine''. 178\u2013205.\n* [[Nur-eldeen Masalha|Masalha, Nur]] (1992). ''[[Expulsion of the Palestinians: The Concept of 'Transfer' in Zionist Political Thought, 1882\u20131948]]'', [[Institute for Palestine Studies]], {{ISBN|978-0-88728-235-5}}\n* [[Ilan Papp\u00e9|Pappe, Ilan]] (2006), ''[[The Ethnic Cleansing of Palestine]]'', [[Oneworld Publications]], Oxford, England, {{ISBN|978-1-85168-467-0}}\n* Reiter, Yitzhak, \"National Minority, Regional Majority: Palestinian Arabs Versus Jews in Israel\" (''Syracuse Studies on Peace and Conflict Resolution''), (2009) Syracuse Univ Press (Sd). {{ISBN|978-0-8156-3230-6}}\n* Sheleg, Yair (2001). [https://web.archive.org/web/20051204222100/http://www.haaretzdaily.com/hasen/pages/ShArt.jhtml?itemNo=101419 \"A Short History of Terror]\" ''[[Haaretz]]''.\n* Zertal, Idith (2005). ''Israel's Holocaust and the Politics of Nationhood''. Cambridge: [[Cambridge University Press]]. {{ISBN|978-0-521-85096-4}}\n\n===Fiction===\n* ''[[The Hope (novel)|The Hope]]'' by [[Herman Wouk]], a historical novel that includes a fictionalized version of Israel's War of Independence.\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|1948 Arab-Israeli War}}\n* [http://www.jpost.com/Defense/Article.aspx?id=277611 One of last surviving founders of IAF recalls mission that stopped Egypt from advancing on Tel Aviv.]\n* [http://www.israelvets.com/pictorialhist_air_force.html Pictorial History: Air Force Volunteers.]\n* {{YouTube|HHmBiATUono|Overview of The 1948 Israeli War of Independence (documentary)}}\n* {{You